prompt:
Add a public class called EventPublisher to Domain.calr with an event and a method to subscribe a handler to it.

Use this exact Calor event subscription syntax:
§CL{c001:EventPublisher:pub}
  §EVT{OnDataReceived:EventHandler:pub}
  §MT{m001:Subscribe:pub}
    §I{EventHandler:handler}
    §O{void}
    §SUB OnDataReceived handler
  §/MT{m001}
§/CL{c001}

The event syntax:
- §EVT{name:type:visibility} declares an event
- §SUB eventName handler subscribes a handler to an event
- Events use delegates for handler types
